\title{Connected space (clopen)}
\date{2023-09-04}
\taxon{definition}

\p{
  A topological space #{X} is \em{connected} if for any subset #{A \subseteq X},
  if #{A} is clopen then #{A} is either the empty set #{\emptyset} or the entire
  set #{X}.
}

\p{
  Classically, this definition is equivalent to the [separation definition of
  connectedness](axt-000E).
}
